    <item>
      <title>伊朗在准备对特朗普的信的答复时拒绝我们的威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/iran-rebuffs-us-threats-while-preparing-reply-to-trump-s-letter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗的最高领导人重申了对美国及其盟友的警告，他们将无法通过威胁迫使他的国家进行谈判，并誓言对任何美国侵略的“严厉打击”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/iran-rebuffs-us-threats-while-preparing-reply-to-trump-s-letter</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 09:29:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亲北京纸敦促李卡ing伸向巴拿马港口销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/pro-beijing-paper-urges-li-ka-shing-to-scrap-panama-port-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家亲北京的报纸已呼吁CK Hutchison Holdings Ltd.退出协议，将其在巴拿马运河上的港口出售给Blackrock Inc.领导的集团，这标志着对亿万富翁Li Ka-shawh的压力运动的升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/pro-beijing-paper-urges-li-ka-shing-to-scrap-panama-port-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 07:10:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏丹军队从叛军民兵中夺回总统宫殿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/sudanese-army-enters-presidential-palace-reuters-reports-m8ieowt8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏丹的军队从叛军快速支持的准军事组织喀土穆（Khartoum）撤回了首都喀土穆（Khartoum）的总统宫殿，该组织在一场残酷的内战中战斗了两年。]]></description>
