      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:35:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2023年以来，在土耳其骚动中，里拉的头部最糟糕的每周下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其里拉（Lira）在近两年内每周最陡峭的下降，随着紧急利率的增加未能阻止这种货币在越来越多的政治紧张局势中停止撤退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/lira-set-for-worst-weekly-drop-since-2023-amid-turkey-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平回复特朗普关税后，关键金属跃升了500％</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/a-critical-metal-jumps-500-after-xi-replies-to-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[bismuth＆mdash;从油漆到防御工业的行业中使用的利基金属；自2月初以来，北京触发了出口路缘以回应美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的贸易攻势，从而引起了人们的注意。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/a-critical-metal-jumps-500-after-xi-replies-to-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:06:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国的支出计划重新点燃了外围债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/germany-s-spending-plan-reignites-jitters-over-periphery-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国的大型支出的新时代是在整个欧洲增加借贷成本，重新激起了大陆外围的财政稳定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/germany-s-spending-plan-reignites-jitters-over-periphery-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国具有里程碑意义的支出法案面临最终障碍：值得关注的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/german-landmark-spending-bill-faces-final-hurdle-what-to-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国在债务资助的国防和基础设施支出中释放数千亿欧元的举动预计将在周五通过其最终立法障碍，当时柏林上议院的议员在柏林对措施进行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/german-landmark-spending-bill-faces-final-hurdle-what-to-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普否认NYT报告说，马斯克将在中国战争计划上进行简报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/elon-musk-to-see-secret-us-plan-for-possible-china-war-nyt-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）否认了《纽约时报》（New York Times）的一份报告，称埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）将于周五向美国军方的应急计划进行简报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-21/elon-musk-to-see-secret-us-plan-for-possible-china-war-nyt-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 21 Mar 2025 01:47:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国欢迎与特朗普一致的参议员，贸易谈判停滞不前</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/china-to-welcome-trump-aligned-senator-with-trade-talks-stalled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平总统的政府将欢迎与唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）接近的美国参议员在中国进行会谈，因为世界上最大的经济体试图推动贸易谈判的停滞较低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-20/china-to-welcome-trump-aligned-senator-with-trade-talks-stalled</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 20 Mar 2025 10:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
